‚ßÖ-degen' : Pushout őĒ¬≤-diagonal src-őĒ~‚ĖĶ ‚Üí ‚ßÖ-degen-top
‚ßÖ-degen' = Pushout-assoc‚Üí őĒ¬≤-diagonal őĒ¬≤-diagonal (_, i0) !

