  ‚ßÖ-degen‚ÜźőĒ¬≤-is-segal-equiv {Q = Q} qpc
    = is-equiv-‚ąė
        {f = fst}
        {_‚Čä_.fwd cocone-repr‚Čä ‚ąė cocone-map _ pushout ‚ąė precomp Q ‚ßÖ-degen'}
        (singleton-fst-is-equiv
